                     <interp inst="t17760522-32-person421" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            .</p>
               <p>Middlesex, to wit.</p>
               <p>"The information of</p>
               <p>"
               <persName id="t17760522-32-person422">
                  Joseph
                   Pierson
               <interp inst="t17760522-32-person422" type="surname" value="Pierson"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17760522-32-person422" type="given" value="Joseph"></interp>
