            </rs>.</p>
               <p>HENMAN <rs id="t17760522-32-verdict146" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17760522-32-verdict146" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. <rs id="t17760522-32-punish147" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17760522-32-punish147" type="punishmentCategory" value="death"></interp>
